    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Purpose",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "# VM Rollup Test Suite\n\nThis dashboard compares raw all-time queries against daily rollup test metrics in the `test_evcc_*` namespace. The queries intentionally filter only on `db=\"evcc\"` so imported history without a `host` label and newer live data can be analyzed together.\n\nExpected use:\n- import the dashboard before writing production rollups\n- write a small backfill into `test_evcc_*` only\n- compare raw and rollup curves, totals and shape\n- decide afterwards whether monthly rollups are still needed\n\nIf the rollup metrics are not written yet, all rollup panels will show `No data`. That is expected."
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.3.3"
    },
