        "content": "Raw latest-day PV is available in the comparison chart below via a hostless query. The compact mini-card was removed because the current VictoriaMetrics Grafana plugin does not render this anonymous aggregate reliably in a top-row summary panel.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.3.3"
    },
